14
00:00:32.066 --> 00:00:35.100
Come back often after you take my gift.

15
00:00:35.100 --> 00:00:36.633
All right, my dear.

16
00:00:36.700 --> 00:00:37.966
Be good.

17
00:01:03.966 --> 00:01:05.433
You little thing

18
00:01:05.466 --> 00:01:06.733
Usually don't let me touch it

19
